snippet.title: Government Returning 50 Per Cent Black Money To Hoarders: Rahul Gandhi

localized.description:
Congress vice-president Rahul Gandhi today accused the government of helping black money hoarders with the amendment to the income tax law, saying half of the unaccounted cash would now be returned to them. The government has given 50 per cent of the black money back to hoarders again, he said outside Parliament.
